<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Kazarius</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-05-21 06:41:47</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>**Quick Update**<BR>
<BR>
Finally landed a Crippling blow.<BR>
It hit for (348) but did 362 dmg with my lvl bonus.<BR>
<BR>
Need to clarify on the normal max dmg with non buffed str.<BR>
The 130's i mentioned in the previous post is the upper extreme, the normal 100+ hits are anywhere from 112 to 120'ish, low 130's is about the max for a near 180'ish str. But of course those 12 dmg slashes occassionaly show up lol. It proc'ed for me 10 to 12 times during a fight with a yellow mob tonite, dex was buffed to about 160 but it was a VERY long fight coz I was in a small group fighting a major mob.<BR>
<BR>
I've only had it for 2 weeks, I'm sure those numbers will change, but hope my posts help give you an idea of its performance.<BR>
<BR>
-kaz</font></td></tr></table>
